Trade/Device Name(s): FORA V10 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
FORA V10 Blood Glucose Monitoring System, Model TD-4244
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): FORA V10 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for the FORA V10 Blood Glucose Monitoring System, a home and professional-use device for quantitative blood glucose measurement using an electrochemical biosensor.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from finger and alternative sites in people with diabetes mellitus and healthcare professionals as an aid in monitoring diabetes control; not for diagnosis or screening of diabetes or for use on neonates.
